      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DEFENDER (1) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind Rockin' Kinloch (23.17) in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to give a sight. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Good form should continue. FLETCHER KEEPING (8) was an impressive winner last time in quickest of the meeting when scoring by 0.8 lengths (22.70) at this track. This tougher but expected to be in the finish. WAVE OF FUN (7) jumped well to win over the 300m at this track two runs back then settled forward again when finishing second at this track last start. Boasts three wins from five starts out of this box. Expected to feature again. INCREDIBLE HEART (4) placed here at this trip last start - cannot be ignored.",
